@Ford Farm Coastal Cheddar{1} makes up the winning selection for our delicious
cheese board, along with @Fourme D'ambert{1}, @Wensleydale & Cranberry{1}, and
@French Camembert{1}.

Serve with @Millers Damsel Charcoal Wafers{1} crackers and @Quince Fruit
Chutney{1}.

